. The acceleration due to gravity in the vicinity of earth surface is a constant and should not change because of the acceleration of the lift.
 </item>
<item> The weight of the block is mg = 10 x 10 = 100 N.
 </item>
<item> The block is acted upon by a normal force, N, as applied by the floor of the lift in upwards direction.
 </item>
</list>
</para>
