 (This does not change in the vicinity of Earth).
</item>
<item> The weight of the block is mg = 10 x 10 = 100 N. This is based on the fact that mass of the block is 10 kg. Hence, weight, mg = 10 X 10 = 100 N.
 </item>
</list>
</para>
