<section id="section-4">
<title> Theoretical basis of analysis in accelerated frame </title>
<para id="element-54">The conception of pseudo force in an accelerated frame of reference is not without basis. We can develop the theoretical framework that justifies using additional force in accelerated frame for applying Newton’s second law. 
</para>
<para id="element-55">Here, we consider a body “A” of mass “m”. An external force “<term>F</term>” acts on the body as shown. The acceleration of the body with respect to ground, “
